de.ityx.mediatrix.data

Class Subproject

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.ityx.mediatrix.data.ErpsData
      • de.ityx.mediatrix.data.Subproject
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IErpsData, IViewFilterDefinition, Serializable

    public class Subproject
extends ErpsData
implements IViewFilterDefinition
    All incoming emails(questions) are assigned to a subproject. Furthermore are technical quality specifications like service level and escalation bound to individual subprojects. The subproject is a part of a project. It's 1:n relation. The subproject belongs to only one project. The project has at least one subproject.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
    was:
    Teilprojekt
